data.title: Sensation
data.copy: Close your eyes and take a few deep breaths. Feel the sensations in the bottom of your feet.

data.title: Sensation
data.copy: Close your eyes and take a few deep breaths Place your attention on your hands. Feel the sensations there.

data.title: Sensation
data.copy: Close your eyes and take a few breaths. What are you feeling in your torso? Pay close attention to the sensations there.

data.title: Sensation
data.copy: Close your eyes and take a few breaths. What are you feeling in your forehead? Pay close attention to the sensations there.

data.title: Sensation
data.copy: Close your eyes and take a few breaths. Start from your feet and move your attention through your body. Pause for a breath at your knees, groin, stomach, chest, neck, and head.

data.title: Sensation
data.copy: Close your eyes and take a few breaths. What are you feeling in your eyes? Pay close attention to the sensations there.

data.title: Sensation
data.copy: Close your eyes and feel the entire surface of your back.

data.title: Sensation
data.copy: Close your eyes and feel the tips of your toes. Bring your attention back to the area if you get distracted.
